import React from 'react';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import FloatingLabel from 'react-bootstrap/FloatingLabel'

import {Row, Col, Button} from 'react-bootstrap';


const Pagos = () => {
    return (
        <Row className="g-2">
            <Col md>
                <FloatingLabel controlId="floatingInputGrid" label="Monto de la transacción">
                <Form.Control type="number" placeholder="monto"/>
                </FloatingLabel>
            </Col>
            <Col md>
                <FloatingLabel controlId="floatingSelectGrid" label="Seleccione el tipo de movimiento">
                <Form.Select aria-label="Floating label select example">
                    <option value="1">Pago por alquiler</option>
                    <option value="2">Pago por venta</option>
                    <option value="3">Entrada</option>
                    <option value="4">Salida</option>
                </Form.Select>
                </FloatingLabel>
            </Col>
            <Col md>
                <FloatingLabel controlId="floatingInputGrid" label="CBU Transaccionado">
                <Form.Control type="string" placeholder="CBU"/>
                </FloatingLabel>
            </Col>
            <Col xs="auto">
                <Button type="submit" className="btn-customize mb-2">
                    Registrar Transaccion
                </Button>
            </Col>
            <Col xs="auto">
                <Button type="submit" className="btn-customize mb-2">
                    Cerrar caja del día
                </Button>
            </Col>
        </Row>
  );
}

export default Pagos;
